node.text:
How weekends should always look like with @jeremyaustiin at the One&Only Mandarina. 🍃 We don’t mind extending a weekender in Mexico to a whole week if it means having these incredible views! 🇲🇽 

📸 @jeremyaustiin and @rupertpeace 
📍 Riviera Nayarit, Mexico
